sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Telegram
    participant API as Creova API
    participant Assistant as Prompt Assistant
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Worker
    participant Renderer as Image Renderer
    participant Storage

    User->>Telegram: Send simple image idea
    Telegram->>API: Update
    API->>DB: Authorize and persist draft
    API->>Assistant: Assess structured brief
    Assistant-->>API: Brief patch or one question
    API-->>Telegram: Ask clarification or show review
    User->>Telegram: Confirm draft version
    Telegram->>API: Confirmation callback
    API->>DB: Reserve budget and create one job
    API-->>Telegram: Queued acknowledgement
    Worker->>DB: Claim job with lease
    Worker->>Renderer: Generate confirmed image
    Renderer-->>Worker: Image output
    Worker->>Storage: Validate and store privately
    Worker->>DB: Persist asset and delivery event
    Worker-->>Telegram: Deliver image and publishing-later notice
